name: Stickmen God
description:
Stickmen God is a game where you take place as the god of small stickmen people, and you can most certainly torture them with tools such as Gravity Shift, Spin Objects, and Collider Manager, plus when you have the chance try to pull them apart.

- By Nocrom Studios 

- Oreo Osborn you know who you are
